@startuml GuideAssignmentExecutionFlow
title Guide Assignment / Execution & Attendance / Incident & Completion

skinparam swimlaneWidth same
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam activityBorderColor #2F6FED
skinparam conditionStyle diamond

|#LightBlue|Staff|
|#Lavender|System|
|#LightBlue|Tour Guide|
|#Wheat|Customer|

|Staff|
:Step 1: Assign Tour Guide to Schedule;

|System|
:Step 2: Save TourAssignment Record\nand send notification;

|Tour Guide|
:Step 3: Receive notification\nand access dashboard;

|Customer|
:Step 4: Arrive at meeting point;

|Tour Guide|
:Step 5: Check customer attendance;

|System|
:Step 6: Record attendance data;

|Tour Guide|
:Step 7: Update tour status to In-Progress;

|System|
:Step 8: Update schedule status in DB\nstatus = IN_PROGRESS;

|Tour Guide|
:Step 9: Log operation\nand report incidents;

|System|
:Step 10: Save incident and operation logs;

|Tour Guide|
:Step 11: Update tour status to Completed;

|System|
:Step 12: Update schedule status to Completed\nstatus = COMPLETED;

|Customer|
:Step 13: Submit tour review and rating;

stop

@enduml
